[[Translation:en/Archive/OpenTTD/Comparison of OpenTTD and TTDPatch features]]
If you have played TTDPatch a lot, you will notice that many similar things are implemented differently in OpenTTD. Not all features are [[en/Manual/Interoperability|compatible]] with TTDPatch.
*[[en/Manual/Interoperability|Quick savegame conversion guide]]

